[normal]shows the number of pedal cyclists who have been killed
[normal] or seriously injured 
[normal](KSI) 
[normal]in Great
[normal] Britain in the years 2002 to 2012. The t
[normal]able also shows an estimate of the number of billion kilometres cycled derived from the National Travel Survey (
[normal]and 
[normal]using 
